The first of Lawrence's three grandchildren, he is now a tenor saxophonist based in Los Angeles.
Lawrence's other two grandchildren, Sarah Hunt and Tom Clatworthy, are both residents of the United Kingdom.
It was originally telecast in the United States on CBS on 23 September 2002 as the season premiere.
